+### 14.1 Direct Competitor Comparison Table
+
+| Feature | Yutori | Thedi | Feedly Leo | Elicit | Perplexity Pro | Zapier Interfaces | Bardeen.ai | Clay.com |
+|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
